title: IAA Tonight | New York Football is Back AND Steelers Stump Brady and the Bucs
description: The Giants and the Jets have New York football fans excited about their teams again after the Giants defeated 2019 MVP Lamar Jackson and the Ravens, and the Jets defeated reigning MVP Aaron Rodgers and the Packers. Leger Douzable, Adam Pacman Jones and Brandon Flowers discuss what has attributed to the turnaround for both teams. Plus, Tom Brady was spotted at Robert Kraft's wedding on Friday, but should he have been in Pittsburgh preparing for the game instead?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Pacman Jones, Brandon Flowers)
